text: The Jiabao V52 is a five- to eight-seater Microvan made by FAW Jilin under the Jiabao sub-brand. ==Overview== FAW Jiabao V52 rear Launched in 2011, the Jiabao V52 was powered by either a 48 hp 1.0 liter Inline-four petrol engine or a 58 hp 1.0 liter Inline-four petrol engine. With the Jiabao V52 priced between 27,200 yuan and 29,200 yuan. ==Jiabao V55== The Jiabao V52 also spawned a 304mm longer version called the Jiabao V55 with a single model priced at 32,900 yuan and powered by the same engine.
